ExecDesc.value: Microsoft Works Word Document Processing Use After Free(IPv6_Version)

EngDesc.value: A vulnerability has been reported in Microsoft Works that could allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary code on the vulnerable system. The vulnerability is due to an error while parsing Word files which can lead to heap corruption. Remote attackers could exploit this vulnerability by persuading a target user to open a specially crafted Word file in a vulnerable application. Successful exploitation would result in execution of arbitrary code with the privileges of the logged in user.
